00:42:06.776 --> 00:42:09.256
and something strange
happens [INAUDIBLE]..

00:42:09.256 --> 00:42:11.240
AUDIENCE: Do you
consider [INAUDIBLE]??

00:42:18.680 --> 00:42:23.510
YUJIN NAGASAWA: So miracles are
