00:42:23.510 --> 00:42:25.470
And if you experience
something really,

00:42:25.470 --> 00:42:27.440
really weird,
actually you might not

00:42:27.440 --> 00:42:30.290
want to tell anyone
because it's so strange,

00:42:30.290 --> 00:42:32.700
and you don't want people
