00:42:45.714 --> 00:42:46.890
AUDIENCE: Hi.

00:42:46.890 --> 00:42:48.180
Thanks for your talk.

00:42:48.180 --> 00:42:50.010
So you mentioned earlier
that young people

00:42:50.010 --> 00:42:54.340
would be more inclined
