00:43:19.350 --> 00:43:20.580
decides to make it rain.

00:43:20.580 --> 00:43:22.200
Or we say, actually, no.

00:43:22.200 --> 00:43:23.260
This is how it works.

00:43:23.260 --> 00:43:24.900
This is how the weather works?

00:43:24.900 --> 00:43:27.960
YUJIN NAGASAWA: So when I say
